ehthumbs.db
ehthumbs_vista.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/
*.cab
*.msi
*.msix
*.msm
*.msp
*.lnk

## Linux
*~
.Trash-*
.nfs*
.directory
.*.sw[a-p]

# Editor/IDE-Specific Ignores (common for Unity devs)

## Visual Studio / Visual Studio Code
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
*.code-workspace

## JetBrains (Rider, IntelliJ)
.idea/**
*.iml

# Miscellaneous
*.stackdump
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight